    Function ConcatAlternate(slice1, slice2):
    Initialize result as an empty slice
    Initialize i, j as 0 (index pointers for slice1 and slice2)
    Get the lengths of slice1 and slice2 (len1 and len2)

    If len1 > len2:
        While i < len1 or j < len2:
            If i < len1, append slice1[i] to result and increment i
            If j < len2, append slice2[j] to result and increment j
    
    Else if len1 < len2:
        While i < len1 or j < len2:
            If j < len2, append slice2[j] to result and increment j
            If i < len1, append slice1[i] to result and increment i
    
    Else:
        While i < len1 or j < len2:
            If i < len1, append slice1[i] to result and increment i
            If j < len2, append slice2[j] to result and increment j

    Return result

    
    
