Function Inter(str1, str2):
    If length of str1 is 0 OR length of str2 is 0:
        Return ""

    Initialize an empty string result
    Initialize an empty map seen

    For each character char in str1:
        If char exists in str2 AND char is not in seen:
            Append char to result
            Mark char as seen in the map

    Print result followed by a newline


